Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直像迷宫一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心别走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.14,0:01:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:01:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甘…甘油炸药？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 这些全受潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 不会爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道追兵几时会来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴风雪好像过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金布利和中央来的部下共计3名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找准破绽解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战计划仅由这里在场人员执行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对北方司令部的士兵也要严格保密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…迈尔斯少校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说解决掉 难道是要杀了他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不赞成杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封住他的炼金术 让他交待情报比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为他会乖乖招供吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放他活着太危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他的部下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说不定也是被迫变成合成兽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法才服从他的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只是「说不定」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为怀疑就杀人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷文中将那件事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来还有其他方法的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了布里格斯的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍一大意就会没命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那种天真的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定会断送你和同伴的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不需要愚钝之人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会收拾掉金布利及其他两人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说都是个小孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世界想贯彻不杀真是太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我也有过那种时期呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了这年纪 久经沙场就会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不杀人比杀人还困难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔利克兄弟选择了困难的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是些好事之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不过我也有点羡慕他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个「拉萨亚纳」是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让人长寿的灵药
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是说贤者之石吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…「将一切金属变成金 返老还童」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个「奥雷利安」呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是金的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长生不老总是和金有联系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为写这本书的斯卡的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到了新国炼丹术影响吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此话怎讲？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们新国
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不死之人就是真正的人 被称为「真人」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思就是「完全的人」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金也是完全的金属
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也有把「真人」叫做「金人」的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全的人就是金人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另有一说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为把炼金术传到新国的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个金发金瞳长生不老的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才这么叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金发金瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像爱德和阿尔一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 大家快来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是出口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺利穿过山脉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在赶往布里格斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 你们都跟我来…哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪好深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,435)\fs23}（HELP ME）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 我背你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,435)\fs23}（喂喂 HELP ME）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把雪踩实开道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,435)\fs23}（没人听见吗）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们跟在后面就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,435)\fs23}（喂喂 HELP ME）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（喂～～）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（喂～HELP ME～）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（有人吗～）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 糟糕糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不小心陷到坑里 结果就被埋住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爬过山先过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爬山？在那暴风雪中？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不绕道直接过来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有紧急联络
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急联络？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央军进入了布里格斯要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯特朗少将也被召去中央了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在去要塞很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只好藏去别处了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别处是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离这里不远应该有个叫阿斯别克的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说我有些同胞藏身在那里的贫民窟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊修瓦尔的贫民窟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来也别无选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是老大 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔突然不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金布利不会起疑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事 哥哥会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第3班 3名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第4班 5名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 人齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 开始分头搜索各自负责的地区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是　明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 阿尔冯斯君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里要说「好」才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 但是这个行动好不方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喏 金布利看过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 金布利他们要搜索哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城中心有个大纵坑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像要从那里进去调查坑道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是北方兵不可信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只带中央的部下去查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啧 那家伙发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先绕过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在纵坑附近占好狙击点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在坑道入口找找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有复数的足迹就没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这距离可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华君…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:09:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金布利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要调查坑道的话交给布里格斯兵比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面好像很复杂的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会特地前来拖住我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来就是这里没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想快点找到斯卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么你是在狙击手占好位之前来拖时间的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围杀气这么重 当然会发现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没白从伊修瓦尔战中生还啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们好像在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能只瞄准金布利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪 慎重点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那混账 用雪遮挡视线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金布利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啧 大叔你们也是合成兽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过对方也一样 半斤八两…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我老实点 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么差的视野条件下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别想逃过我们灵敏的嗅觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢仔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪 说句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈尔斯少校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有合成兽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们习惯在视野不良的地方战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要进到雪雾里来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 可恶又要变矮了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甘油炸药？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是矿山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 不要靠近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道这是什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些东西早就受潮没法用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 你们知道甘油炸药的原料是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硝化甘油？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硝化甘醇还有木屑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有硝酸铵什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么硝酸铵是怎么生成的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很简单 硝酸和氨…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氨？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是氨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻子太灵有时候也不是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这帮家伙已经没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦不用担心人质就反了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想让你把知道的所有事情都给我吐出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是血气方刚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚大病初愈 要对付年轻人还真要命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我也没工夫跟你耗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我用一下这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然主动亮出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能使用炼成阵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:14:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真这么认为？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决心不杀人的确是了不起的方针
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在战场上这会成为软肋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那一瞬你没给我致命一击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种幼稚导致了你的失败
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纵坑塌方了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真狠心 连我们一起砸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金布利那家伙去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 又被拖走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？ 被拖走？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,435)\fs23}喂 怎么了 穿盔甲的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂…被拖到那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔！阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂被拖走？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 之前发生过类似事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 阿尔 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能这样让她流泪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的金布利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 钢仔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要救我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明自己伤得更重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要搞错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要有人把刺入腹部的东西拔出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我们把那根钢筋拔出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可还是敌人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也没有命令我们杀死你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 拔出来的话你会立即大出血而死的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔出来的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大出血之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会用炼金术封住伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有医疗方面炼金术的经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我想进行人体练成的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微研究过个大概
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在你内脏严重受损啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你又不像金布利先生有贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有贤者之石可以用我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寿命可能会稍微缩短点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我自己的幼稚招致的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要自己来收拾残局
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不大清楚状况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但确实没时间犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拔了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己的生命看做一种能量体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和贤者之石一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我现在就是一个灵魂份的贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的…感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用人命的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别随便把人杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有完全治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是把没伤的组织连起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勉强止血的应急处理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那得赶紧让医生看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得赶紧去追金布利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然大家都…有危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这状态打起来完全没胜算的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是金布利先生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要用敬语了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个变态
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把我们也卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 就此跟那个混蛋划清界限了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.20,0:22:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就当我们在这里死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是自由身了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…这家伙怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.69,0:22:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让他死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹是我们的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.47,0:22:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.67,0:22:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去以后赶快找医生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.59,0:22:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.19,0:24:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为打破僵局 开辟道路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要奇思妙想与行动力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.30,0:24:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了隐藏着的真实的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.81,0:24:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌握着通往胜利的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.00,0:24:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 这是日积月累的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.19,0:24:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.85,0:24:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第42话 反击的先兆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.64,0:24:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻 战争即将爆发
